summary:
The AcceleDrome is an underground racing facility featured in the Hot Wheels universe, where the Teku and Metal Maniacs teams train for the World Race. Located within Dr. Tezla’s headquarters, it combines cave-like architecture with advanced technology. At its center is a holographic "Wheel of Power." Key vehicles associated with the environment include Rat-ified (Metal Maniacs), Chicane (Teku), Spine Buster (Mark Wylde), and Vert Wheeler’s high-performance car.

This DLC includes:
1 Environment to build your tracks: AcceleDrome;
4 Vehicles: Rat-ified, Chicane, Spine Buster, Vert’s;
1 new area to add to the Hot Wheels Creature Rampage mode;
Background, Profile icon, Tag and Card Background.
